title: Do You Spy on Your Partner
itunes:title: Do You Spy on Your Partner
description:
Today on the show The Breakfast Club was joined by Tamika Mallory, Minister Kirstin Jon Foye and Mysonne stopped by and spoke about systematic injustice, soiled politics and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a doctor that accidentally circumcised a man. Moreover, we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners spy on their partners after Reginae admitted that she went to a party to spy on her ex.
